{"tid":1246213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小心不法分子】資訊安全 （Location History, VPN, etc.)","createTime":"2019-06-20T15:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T15:47:23.000Z","uid":160758,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff9c231800a3cca786dd891a92eb64a7a29eb378","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"如果手機、電腦俾不法分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入侵，咁就冇喇。所以想喺度提提大家資訊安全嘅重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(唔明用詞請自行Google)<br />\n<br />\nEFF: <a href=\"https://www.eff.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eff.org%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=2242ac20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eff.org/</a><br />\nPrivacytools .io: <a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=b6eda03a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺網上，真名個人資料就梗係唔好出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n密碼嗰啲就基本啦(alphabet + numbers + special characters) (at least 16 characters)，盡量唔好重復用密碼<br />\n<br />\nGoogle, Facebook, etc. 有得開2-Factor Verification就開啦<br />\n<br />\n電腦：<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft Windows有人話唔安全：<a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/operating-systems/#win10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2Foperating-systems%2F%23win10&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=ff6b28e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/operating-systems/#win10</a><br />\n咁最好用Mac/Linux啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請del任何敏感資訊!!</strong>: <a href=\"https://securityinabox.org/en/guide/destroy-sensitive-information/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecurityinabox.org%2Fen%2Fguide%2Fdestroy-sensitive-information%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=62edf23a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://securityinabox.org/en/guide/destroy-sensitive-information/</a><br />\n<br />\n請加密電腦:<br />\nMacOS: FileVault2<br />\nWindows: 唔知<br />\nLinux:  ...用得Linux都係大佬...自己揾啦<br />\n<br />\n加密documents: VeraCrypt<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/software/encryption-tools/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2Fsoftware%2Fencryption-tools%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=435625b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/software/encryption-tools/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle (特別係Android) ：<br />\n記得上：<a href=\"https://myaccount.google.com/data-and-personalization去保護你哋資料\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyaccount.google.com%2Fdata-and-personalization%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E4%BD%A0%E5%93%8B%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=7acb75e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myaccount.google.com/data-and-personalization去保護你哋資料</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其係location history，俾啲不法分子睇到就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jxiu9jV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxiu9jV.png&h=af36cee4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n啲外國勢力諗邪惡梗係要pause能晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIOS：<br />\n<br />\n唔好開Face id/Touch id就梗啦，一陣啲不法分子夾硬開就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開埋Erase Data就更好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9JSnPP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9JSnPP.jpg&h=958e1cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去完咩地方，記得去General-&gt;Reset-&gt;Reset Location &amp; Privacy嚟清除個人嘅location history<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9a8KYgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9a8KYgf.jpg&h=0f903a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熄埋佢就最穩陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fo9Vkv0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffo9Vkv0.jpg&h=3eda727b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nCamera都係呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boybDii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FboybDii.jpg&h=08e04f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSocial Media:<br />\n1. Post少兩日ig facebook snapchat (etc.) 唔駛死嘅<br />\n2. 對話記錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (<span style=\"color: red;\">正常</span>就唔駛del嘅)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nVPN:<br />\n唔想俾外國勢力check到ip? 記得用VPN（推薦ProtonVPN）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBrowser:<br />\nHide咗你個ip address唔等於安全，請用Firefox/<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Tor Browser</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n刪晒啲Browsing History同cookies就一定，長開埋Private Browsing就仲safe<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4L5YikM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4L5YikM.png&h=734b1a73&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想安全請del browser fingerprinting:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/browsers/#fingerprint\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2Fbrowsers%2F%23fingerprint&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=c5c52b32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/browsers/#fingerprint</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有WebRC IP Leak Test: <a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/browsers/#webrtc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2Fbrowsers%2F%23webrtc&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=783b39c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/browsers/#webrtc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機：<br />\n用華為小米(etc.)就<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最安全</strong></span>㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nInstant Messenger:<br />\n請避免Whatsapp（not open sourced)，請轉用TG/Signal(推)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/software/im/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2Fsoftware%2Fim%2F&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=82f90956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/software/im/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他：<br />\n-小心使用Cloud Service (Google Documents, Microsoft OneDrive, Office365)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">-用腦</span></span><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 歡迎Android用家幫手補充"},{"pid":"46386f8019ffc5e8d04c813c8561bb46b91b176b","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:21:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de5891f954ecc841196f4471b89250b28de416e","tid":1246213,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"【請為621廣泛報料，聽朝七點，政總集合】<br />\n【不內哄、不分化、各自上山、空城計更佳】<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>======20/6/2019 17:00更新======</strong></span><br />\n立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府警察勢力分報圖，持續收料，一直更新。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rtOBOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rtOBOy.jpg&h=eae4919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n<strong>更多細節請用追故模式</strong><br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34yGdCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34yGdCf.jpg&h=2aced7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gB8C11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gB8C11.jpg&h=f5e08abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aA1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aA1c0.jpg&h=0cd9b552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮賓府交通路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1.急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n2.立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港親共商店地圖</span></span></strong><br />\n消費前，睇下呢個地圖！斷親共收入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IKNf97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IKNf97&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=3dd8b92c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IKNf97</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48889ad02bd27a13b02f2f364242cb804d87320d","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ff85a45a9ea9433fa1dced1cf74aef66104c1dd","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"Disclaimer: 純分享"},{"pid":"56d0f2738867b964b90bece4c279f1a524cfaeb0","tid":1246213,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:27:45.000Z","msg":"巴打，我寫咗一大篇資訊安全嘅guide<br />\n睇吓有冇用，包括VPN, Tor, 好多好多<br />\n<br />\n《資訊安全手冊》：香港全民網絡自我防衛指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1235172/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1235172/</a>"},{"pid":"54242a87d8a573346bd7b0b56af7428e03458a27","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56d0f2738867b964b90bece4c279f1a524cfaeb0","tid":1246213,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:27:45.000Z","msg":"巴打，我寫咗一大篇資訊安全嘅guide<br />\n睇吓有冇用，包括VPN, Tor, 好多好多<br />\n<br />\n《資訊安全手冊》：香港全民網絡自我防衛指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1235172/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1235172/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:29:37.000Z","msg":"Thank You, 以為冇人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d311a2c5bd26a42dfcaa3d876613d590377cb2e","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"pushpushpush<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cc1b582559d0089e05f8a343f486a75ebb5344","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e5782f100323266ff55f804dd9a90444c6313ff7","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"pushpush"},{"pid":"75ee3e0086a220efbdbd1220643fec55f7d2a0f0","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa3677cb6e602ca8bbab709657ac686d7cb78b4f","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"60fd435991b5c5f56c3b72a0578cd379681000b1","tid":1246213,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}